"tid":2178159,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90ab2394e36812bae230d9bb69db3392a486a88f","tid":2178159,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:25:25.000Z","msg":"可以沒收番, 比番政府用?! <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:45:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawSingle.aspx?pcode=A0030286&amp;flno=6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flaw.moj.gov.tw%2FLawClass%2FLawSingle.aspx%3Fpcode%3DA0030286%26flno%3D6&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyOCCrfoqRshWq79J%2FX5JLMA%3D&h=b251b9e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawSingle.aspx?pcode=A0030286&amp;flno=6</a><br />\n<br />\n第 6 條<br />\n經本會認定屬不當取得之財產，應命該政黨、附隨組織、受託管理人，或無正當理由以無償或顯不相當對價，自政黨、附隨組織或其受託管理人取得或轉得之人於一定期間內<span class=\"gold\">移轉為國有、地方自治團體或原所有權人所有。</span><br />\n<br />\n前項財產移轉範圍，以移轉時之現存利益為限。但以不相當對價取得者，應扣除取得該財產之對價。<br />\n<br />\n第一項規定之財產，如已移轉他人而無法返還時，應就政黨、附隨組織、其受託管理人或無正當理由以無償或顯不相當對價，自政黨、附隨組織或其受託管理人取得或轉得之人之其他財產<span class=\"gold\">追徵其價額</span>。"},{"pid":"d793fc347a9546a43f8d7e38e2d7b4bcaa219013","tid":2178159,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"345d5d6aad7ebebf2d462b80f20ae6f9f5664040","tid":2178159,"uid":138409,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:17:05.000Z","msg":"有關不當黨產處理委員會 嘅 介紹<br />\n相當清楚<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dGHy3UjfQ_8&amp;list=PLh2f8-dZPV-hWDRMSDPg1xly4CBgQVoPu&amp;index=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdGHy3UjfQ_8%26list%3DPLh2f8-dZPV-hWDRMSDPg1xly4CBgQVoPu%26index%3D1&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyOCCrfoqRshWq79J%2FX5JLMA%3D&h=a7f89102\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dGHy3UjfQ_8&amp;list=PLh2f8-dZPV-hWDRMSDPg1xly4CBgQVoPu&amp;index=1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:46:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawSingle.aspx?pcode=A0030286&amp;flno=6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flaw.moj.gov.tw%2FLawClass%2FLawSingle.aspx%3Fpcode%3DA0030286%26flno%3D6&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyOCCrfoqRshWq79J%2FX5JLMA%3D&h=b251b9e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://law.moj.gov.tw/LawClass/LawSingle.aspx?pcode=A0030286&amp;flno=6</a><br />\n<br />\n第 6 條<br />\n經本會認定屬不當取得之財產，應命該政黨、附隨組織、受託管理人，或無正當理由以無償或顯不相當對價，自政黨、附隨組織或其受託管理人取得或轉得之人於一定期間內移轉為國有、地方自治團體或原所有權人所有。<br />\n<br />\n前項財產移轉範圍，以移轉時之現存利益為限。但以不相當對價取得者，應扣除取得該財產之對價。<br />\n<br />\n第一項規定之財產，如已移轉他人而無法返還時，應就政黨、附隨組織、其受託管理人或無正當理由以無償或顯不相當對價，自政黨、附隨組織或其受託管理人取得或轉得之人之其他財產追徵其價額。"},{"pid":"c733b26df56f3fdefc53d26927fdc430a617ef97","tid":2178159,"uid":138409,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"2c54ba4f63b13bd30b89ed53273878ba5f595d9b","tid":2178159,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"31b8f6466fffdc091b370a993b183ddb66bda631","tid":2178159,"uid":138409,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8aec4c1796b8c3cafe20b40438e2242fde48039c","tid":2178159,"uid":49643,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:22:50.000Z","msg":"民進黨玩到咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要換左新一屆政府先判決"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:40:28.000Z","msg":"終於可以將國民黨掃入垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實單案都幾年前拖到依家㗎啦<br />\n你見係「107年度憲三字第15號」<br />\n即係2018年嗰時 申請釋憲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:45:25.000Z","msg":"但之後又會變DPP獨大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:49:14.000Z","msg":"咁總會有人唔妥DPP<br />\n總會有人另起爐灶嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓粉 過檔新黨 / 統促黨<br />\n九二共識撚就去 親民黨<br />\n搞好經濟撚 就去 民眾黨（雖然之前好似唔多掂<